aka: Catwalk: From Glada Hudik to New York
this_title: Catwalk - från Glada Hudik till New York
trans_title: Catwalk: From Glada Hudik to New York
introduction: Emma wants to become a fashion model and ask Pär Johansson and the Glada Hudik-theatre for help. An unattainable dream for most, especially if you have a disability. Together with a group of unusual models they begin a bewildering journey.
chinese_title: Catwalk - från Glada Hudik till New York
